---
import LandingPage from '../../layouts/LandingPage.astro';
---
<LandingPage 
  title="Port Emission Calculation & Tracking" 
  description="Monitor, analyze, and optimize your maritime emissions with PortTracker's real-time eco-scoring. Drive sustainability across your entire port operation."
  ctaUrl="https://porttracker.co/emissions"
  ctaLabel="View Port Emissions"
>
  <div class="feature-block">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Real-Time Eco-Scoring</h2>
      <p>PortTracker automatically calculates emissions based on real-time AIS data and vessel characteristics. Monitor CO2, NOx, and SOx output dynamically as ships enter and exit your port jurisdiction, ensuring full compliance with maritime environmental standards.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">🌱</div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="feature-block reverse">
    <div class="feature-text">
      <h2>Historical Analysis & Reporting</h2>
      <p>Export comprehensive environmental impact reports. Track your progress toward carbon neutrality over time, compare different vessel classes, and identify the heaviest polluters to enforce better port policies.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-image">📊</div>
  </div>
</LandingPage>
